153
00:09:39,410 --> 00:09:41,240
So what's the deal?

154
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:46,090
Well, that point is then that
at that point or at that point

155
00:09:46,090 --> 00:09:50,430
or at any of these other
points, P of u plus v

